name:                mail-reports
version:             0.2.0.0
synopsis:            A parser library for DMARC and SMTP TLS reports
description:         This library is meant to parse DMARC and TLSRPT aggregated reports from bytestrings, XML documents or streaming bytestrings.
-- bug-reports:
